{"type": "article", "id": 16623, "title": "Model NO.3 山地车", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-27T06:00:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122438BVumK7RyZAp1NEXq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBudnitz 近期推出了超轻钛车架的 Model NO.3 山地车。钛金属材料的车架使得这辆车仅有 3.6 磅（1.6 公斤）重，而 Gates CDX 碳纤维皮带传动系统，也比普通链条更轻。自行车的两根弧形车架，代替了常见的三角支架，也更优雅。此外，所有零件都是来自欧美的主流品牌，以确保优质耐用。 <a href=\"http://budnitzbicycles.com/bicycles/view/no3-titanium\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261439383AcLidmuRJVlMXz8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143939qOp0yVQN2kHIZB6w.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143939a8ePxKupgNyLzZdi.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143940E7tGCDH2oMTmYPvS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143940Ri2KSAptPMNYkOa4.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}